  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large skillet, sauté the sliced onion and minced garlic in butter until softened.",
    "Add the sliced pork shoulder to the skillet and cook until browned.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together the cheese curds, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the cooked onion and pork mixture to the cheese curd mixture and stir until well combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish and top with breadcrumbs.",
    "Bake the casserole in the preheated oven for 25 minutes.",
    "Remove the casserole from the oven and let it rest for 10 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
